name: Turned On Tech 06 - MRI Machine
description: A fun series exploring the lascivious side of technology. Everyone loves to use the latest tech, but this series of work focusses on how the tech likes to be used. For an MRI machine, there's only one goal...to get you in the hole! (copyright) Alternative Aesthetics. For personal non-commercial use only. Find me on Instagram and Twitter @alt_aesthetics
